About our community

Welcome to The Townes at Horton Park, located in Apex, NC. This brand new community offers our newest two and three-story townhome floorplans, featuring 3-4 bedrooms, 2.5-3.5 bathrooms, 2,000+ sq. ft. of living space, 1-2 car garages, second floor decks, designer-curated interior packages, and much more!

As you step inside one of our townhomes, prepare to be captivated by the attention to detail and high-quality finishes throughout. The kitchen, a chef's dream, boasts beautiful shaker-style cabinets, quartz countertops, a ceramic tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and spacious kitchen islands. The open floorplan designs are perfect for entertaining, while the LED lighting adds a modern touch and creates a warm, inviting ambiance. The exterior schemes and elevations of our homes were carefully designed to create a beautiful streetscape that you'll be proud to call home. At The Townes at Horton Park, we understand the importance of modern living. That's why each home is equipped with smart home technology, putting convenience and control at your fingertips. Whether adjusting the temperature or turning on the lights, managing your home has never been easier.

Future community amenities will keep you and your family exploring the outdoors with a community pool and bath house. Located just off Ten-Ten Rd, The Townes at Horton Park's ideal location is minutes from major highways, schools, recreation, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Right around the corner is Knights Play Golf Center, perfect for an afternoon of family fun. Avid golfer? Tee off at Lochmere Golf Club, 3.5 miles away, or Bentwinds Country Club, 8.1 miles away. Nature lovers can explore the outdoors at Historic Yates Mill County Park 9.4 miles away, Lake Johnson Park 9.1 miles away, or Apex Nature Park 9.1 miles away. For the kids, 7.3 miles away is Pleasant Park and 5.8 miles away is Sky Zone Trampoline Park. If youre traveling, Raleigh-Durham International Airport is only 17.2 miles away, seamlessly connecting you to your destination. For residents peace of mind, WakeMed Cary Hospital is just 4.1 miles away.

With its prime location, variety of floorplan offerings, and modern features, The Townes at Horton Park is truly a gem. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it your own. Schedule a tour today!

Area Information

Raleigh - Durham

Finding New Homes in Raleigh, NC from D.R. Horton

When you look for new homes in Raleigh, NC it's ideal to work with home builders in North Carolina that you can trust. D.R. Horton has been committed to providing quality, customized homes since 1978. When you work with the #1 builder in the country, you will find the quality, style and comfort that you are looking for.

No matter what phase of life you're in, we can work with you to find the best fit throughout the Raleigh-Durham area, from quaint and cozy to large and luxurious homes.

Houses in the Raleigh area

Our homes in Raleigh and Durham are full of possibilities, and we have a range of plans and options to meet your needs.

  • Houses range from affordable plans to larger designs. Communities feature convenient floor plans as well as unique exterior features so that your home can reflect your personal style.
  • Our neighborhoods offer a range of amenities that friends and family will enjoy. 
  • D.R. Horton homes are backed by a superb warranty.

Getting to know Raleigh

Raleigh is part of the Research Triangle metropolitan area, also known as The Triangle, which refers to the area's successful research park. This is a vital part of Raleigh's economy, providing many job opportunities for residents. This booming city is filled with not just job opportunities, but fun and entertainment too and the city was on Forbes 2013 list of fastest growing cities and continues to appear on numerous lists of 'best places to live'.

The beautiful downtown area of Old Raleigh, one of the most historic neighborhoods in the city, has a growing business district and is also a great cultural attraction. The growing residential and commercial areas of Midtown and Uptown are also popular among locals. Our homes for sale in Raleigh will all keep you close to these admired attractions and other conveniences that you need. Take a look at our opportunities here and discover just what you've been looking for.

    Strictly Necessary Cookies

    Always Active

    These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.

    Performance Cookies

    These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.

    Social Media Cookies

    These cookies are set by a range of social media services that we have added to the site to enable you to share our content with your friends and networks. They are capable of tracking your browser across other sites and building up a profile of your interests. This may impact the content and messages you see on other websites you visit. If you do not allow these cookies you may not be able to use or see these sharing tools.

    Targeting Cookies

    These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.
